{"title": "Way of the Wind", "description": "From the comfort of the hills of Kentucky traveled Celia and her husband Seth to the desolate prairies of Kansas, where cyclones, tornadoes, and endless wind were to greet them. Always, there was the wind cutting across the plains as the young couple builds their home while working the soil, while Seth awaits the wise men of the east to begin building the magic city where he has staked his territory on the plains.<br/><br/>\nBut sometimes life plays cruel tricks upon us. Sometimes our hopes are dashed by happenstance. Sometimes our greatest dreams born of purest intentions become our deepest tragedies. All too often we seek the calmness and serenity in life only to learn that we have inadvertently walked directly into The Way of the Wind.<br/><br/>\n(Introduction by Roger Melin)", "duration": 14751, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "1781", "name": "Zoe Anderson Norris"}], "coverArt": "http://archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCoverArt18/wind_1205.jpg", "copyright_year": "1911", "genres": ["General Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Roger Melin"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Roger Melin"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Elizabeth Klett"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Betty M."}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "01 - Prologue and Chapter 1", "readers": [2156], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/wayofthewind_rm_librivox/wayofthewind_01_norris_64kb.mp3", "duration": 608}, {"section": 2, "title": "02 - Chapter 2", "readers": [2156], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/wayofthewind_rm_librivox/wayofthewind_02_norris_64kb.mp3", "duration": 607}, {"section": 3, "title": "03 - Chapter 3", "readers": [2156], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/wayofthewind_rm_librivox/wayofthewind_03_norris_64kb.mp3", "duration": 562}, {"section": 4, "title": "04 - Chapter 4", "readers": [2156], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/wayofthewind_rm_librivox/wayofthewind_04_no